attr.title: Alien Pogs From Outer Space
attr.desc: This Bullet Heaven Survival game was made for GBJam11 from Sept 15-25 2023. .
attr.inst: Download any version of the game from  [Itch.io](https://meredosia.itch.io/alien-pogs-from-outer-space), extract the zip file and copy the .rpg file into the the  alienpogs port folder.
